%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20plane%20fire%20that%20sent%208%20people%20to%20the%20hospital%20shows%20why%20airlines%20are%20taking%20battery%20safety%20so%20seriously%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SAS%20Connect%20Airbus%20A320neo%20aircraft%20spotted%20taxiing%20at%20London%20Heathrow%20Airport%20LHR%20in%20front%20of%20the%20terminal%20and%20the%20air%20control%20tower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692042c389026fbb4d0e2162%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20suitcase%20caught%20fire%20on%20an%20SAS%20plane%20in%20Oslo%20last%20month.%3Cp%3ENicolas%20Economou%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20battery%20caught%20fire%20while%20passengers%20were%20boarding%20an%20SAS%20flight%2C%20with%208%20people%20sent%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAirlines%20have%20been%20tightening%20their%20rules%20on%20power%20banks%20since%20a%20large%20fire%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20flights%20have%20been%20diverted%20due%20to%20the%20safety%20risk%20posed%20by%20devices%20that%20go%20missing%20on%20board.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20vigilant%20about%20batteries%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20recent%20fire%20on%20a%20flight%20in%20Norway%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEight%20people%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20a%20battery%20caught%20fire%20in%20someone's%20hand%20luggage%2C%20according%20to%20Norway's%20Accident%20Investigation%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassengers%20were%20still%20boarding%20a%20Scandinavian%20Airlines%20plane%20that%20was%20about%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20the%20Norwegian%20capital%2C%20Oslo%2C%20to%20Bergen%2C%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20October%2014%20but%20came%20to%20light%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20Norwegian%20officials%20announced%20their%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2050%20people%20had%20boarded%20SAS%20Flight%20295%20when%20smoke%20was%20seen%20coming%20from%20a%20suitcase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cabin%20was%20evacuated%20while%20the%20pilots%20put%20on%20oxygen%20masks%20and%20the%20flight%20attendants%20wore%20smoke%20hoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECabin%20crew%20members%20tried%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire%2C%20but%20it%20flared%20up%20again.%20The%20suitcase%20was%20taken%20out%20of%20the%20plane%2C%20where%20the%20fire%20service%20put%20out%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ambulance%20service%20was%20called%2C%20and%20eight%20people%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20observation%20after%20they%20were%20believed%20to%20have%20inhaled%20toxic%20fumes.%20They%20were%20all%20discharged%20within%2048%20hours%2C%20Norwegian%20investigators%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAS%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a14198c-d334-465d-9ae0-46b6c153a32b%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20airlines%20cracking%20down%20on%20power%20banks%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Emirates%20A380%20at%20Dubai%20airport.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3c4da7bb3f854015d15dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Emirates%20A380%20at%20Dubai%20airport.%3Cp%3EEmirates%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safety%20risks%20posed%20by%20lithium-battery%20devices%20have%20grown%20more%20apparent%20this%20year%2C%20with%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-tells-airlines-to-be-stricter-about-power-banks-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairlines%20tightening%20power%20bank%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20some%20flights%20being%20forced%20to%20divert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femirates-power-banks-fire-diversion-lithium-battery-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPower%20banks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20phones%2C%20and%20laptops%20are%20all%20powered%20by%20lithium%20batteries%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20former%20are%20more%20susceptible%20to%20damage%20or%20overcharging.%20This%20can%20result%20in%20thermal%20runaway%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20a%20rapid%20temperature%20increase%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20January%2C%2027%20people%20were%20injured%20when%20an%20Air%20Busan%20flight%20caught%20fire%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20South%20Korea's%20Busan%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plane%20was%20written%20off%2C%20and%20investigators%20pointed%20to%20a%20power%20bank%20as%20the%20source%20of%20the%20fire.%20Then%2C%20the%20South%20Korean%20government%20banned%20passengers%20from%20charging%20power%20banks%20on%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20around%20the%20world%20have%20followed%20suit%20with%20similar%20rules%2C%20including%20Emirates%20and%20Southwest%20Airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20day%20after%20its%20new%20rules%20took%20effect%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-flight-diverted-day-after-new-rules-for-portable-chargers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20flight%20diverted%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20battery%20charger%20started%20smoking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20issued%20a%20safety%20alert%20in%20September%2C%20recommending%20airlines%20ensure%20that%20passengers%20keep%20lithium-battery%20devices%20visible%20and%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20recorded%20over%2060%20incidents%20involving%20lithium%20batteries%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20the%20mere%20risk%20of%20a%20fire%20has%20prompted%20pilots%20to%20turn%20planes%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airlines-flight-u-turns-after-passenger-laptop-falls-hold-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnited%20Airlines%20flight%20U-turned%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20after%20a%20passenger%20dropped%20their%20laptop%20down%20the%20side%20of%20their%20seat%2C%20and%20it%20fell%20into%20the%20cargo%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20meant%20those%20on%20board%20wouldn't%20know%20if%20it%20had%20caught%20fire%20until%20it%20was%20too%20late.%20It's%20the%20same%20reason%20you're%20not%20allowed%20to%20pack%20electronic%20devices%20in%20checked%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20the%20status%20of%20it%2C%20we%20can't%20access%20it%2C%20we%20can't%20see%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20pilots%20told%20air%20traffic%20control%20during%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BSo%20our%20decision%20is%20to%20return%20to%20%5BWashington%5D%20Dulles%20and%20find%20this%20laptop%20before%20we%20can%20continue%20over%20the%20ocean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20incident%20occurred%20just%20five%20weeks%20later%2C%20when%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftransatlantic-united-airlines-diversion-after-passenger-dropped-laptop-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnited%20passenger%20dropped%20a%20laptop%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20flight%20from%20London%20to%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaintenance%20crews%20retrieved%20the%20laptop%2C%20inspected%20the%20aircraft%2C%20and%20the%20flight%20later%20departed%20for%20Washington%20Dulles%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20airline%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattery-fire-airlines-aviation-safety-power-banks-sas-faa-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763727119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692043a7e1a9cbb014deb104%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattery-fire-airlines-aviat