ls%20%26quot%3Btortured%26quot%3B%20by%20her%20departure%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20angry%20and%20hurt.%20She%20said%20at%20the%20WSJ%20CMO%20Council%20Summit%20that%20her%20former%20employees%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20she%20had%20hired%2C%20were%20given%20orders%20not%20to%20contact%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20with%20Est%C3%A9e%20Lauder's%20legal%20team%20that%20day%20in%202016%20and%20deciding%20to%20leave%2C%20Brown%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%20that%20she%20called%20her%20husband%2C%20a%20real-estate%20developer%2C%20who%20met%20her%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20her%20he%20was%20glad%20she'd%20left%20%E2%80%94%20he'd%20been%20waiting%20a%20long%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bget%20a%20little%20bit%26quot%3B%20of%20her%2C%20she%20said.%20Then%20he%20suggested%20they%20turn%20a%20historic%20building%20he%20had%20just%20bought%20into%20a%20hotel%2C%20Brown%20said.%20They%20eventually%20went%20on%20to%20do%20just%20that%2C%20creating%20The%20George%2C%20in%20Montclair%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20days%20following%20her%20exit%2C%20the%20makeup%20founder%20began%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20she%20wanted%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20third%20day%2C%20I%20started%20just%20going%20to%20the%20city%20and%20meeting%20people%20for%20breakfast%20and%20lunches%2C%20because%20I%20never%20had%20time%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said%20at%20the%20WSJ%20CMO%20Council%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20kept%20herself%20busy%2C%20taking%20on%20hobbies%20like%20hip-hop%20dancing%2C%20and%20building%20a%20TikTok%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20to%20dance%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BAny%20wedding%20or%20Bar%20Mitzvah%2C%20I%20don't%20leave%20the%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20started%20to%20take%20on%20new%20projects.%20Richard%20Baker%2C%20who%20was%20owned%20Lord%20%26amp%3B%20Taylor%20at%20the%20time%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20Brown%20and%20suggested%20that%20she%20create%20a%20curated%20shop%20called%20the%20Just%20Bobbi%20Shops.%20In%202019%2C%20MasterClass%20asked%20her%20to%20lead%20its%20first-ever%20makeup%20course.%20She%20also%20earned%20a%20health-coach%20certification%2C%20focused%20on%20her%20own%20wellness%2C%20and%20published%20a%20book%20called%20%26quot%3BBeauty%20from%20the%20Inside%20Out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20hit%20me%3A%20I%20wasn't%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20more%20things%20to%20teach%2C%20and%20the%20world%20had%20changed.%20I%20had%20changed%20since%20I%20left%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20launch%20a%20new%20business%20before%20her%20non-compete%20agreement%20ended%2C%20but%20her%20husband%20wouldn't%20let%20her.%20So%20she%20counted%20down%20the%20days%2C%20even%20purchasing%20a%20charm%20with%20the%20date%20the%20agreement%20was%20set%20to%20expire%20%E2%80%94%20October%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20exact%20month%2C%20she%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fjones-road-beauty-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJones%20Road%20Beauty%2C%20a%20makeup%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20focused%20on%20creating%20%26quot%3Bno-makeup%20makeup%26quot%3B%20looks%20with%20clean%20formulas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbobbi-brown-shares-exit-namesake-brand-aftermath-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763724301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e2f8789026fbb4d0dfe48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbobbi-brown-shares-exit-namesake-brand-aftermath-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bobbi%20Brown%20said%20the%20moments%20after%20her%20exit%20from%20her%20namesake%20brand%20weren't%20easy%2C%20and%20she%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20was%20next