Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-office-near-brian-niccol-newport-beach-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Brian%20Niccol%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20described%20November%206%20as%20the%20official%20start%20of%20the%20company's%20holiday%20season%2C%20as%20Starbucks'%20biggest%20sales%20day%20ever%20in%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7339cf2-fc9f-41e5-8209-1784489c3a4e%5C%22%3EA%20key%20season%20in%20Starbucks'%20broader%20turnaround%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHoliday%20is%20really%20important%20to%20Starbucks'%20business%3B%20seasonally%2C%20it's%20an%20important%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20Sara%20Senatore%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20global%20equity%20research%20and%20senior%20analyst%20covering%20restaurants%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BStarbucks%20is%20intrinsically%20kind%20of%20part%20of%20American%20holidays.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Della%20Penna%2C%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20the%20digital%20advertising%20research%20firm%20InMarket%2C%20framed%20Starbucks'%20holiday%20rollout%20as%20a%20multi-layered%20strategy%3A%20one%20that%20builds%20its%20global%20brand%20identity%2C%20satisfies%20local%20tastes%20through%20its%20regional%20offerings%2C%20and%20captures%20multiple%20forms%20of%20consumer%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20from%20beverages%20to%20merchandise%20to%20gift%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223414%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starbucks'%20China%20menu%20includes%20a%20Toffee%20Nut%20Cheesecake%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691fd0a7abd5e944effb3423%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStarbucks'%20China%20menu%20includes%20a%20Toffee%20Nut%20Cheesecake%3Cp%3EStarbucks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20prior%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-gift-card-holiday-season-2015-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStarbucks%20gift%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20so%20ubiquitous%20that%20as%20many%20as%20one%20in%20seven%20Americans%20received%20them%20as%20a%20gift%20during%20the%20holiday%20season.%20Last%20holiday%20season%2C%20Starbucks'%20Q1%20earnings%20report%20revealed%20that%20its%20US%20gift%20card%20sales%20reached%20%243.5%20billion%2C%20maintaining%20its%20position%20as%20the%20%232%20brand%20in%20the%20US%20by%20gift%20card%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Della%20Penna's%20view%2C%20the%20holiday%20season%20exemplifies%20how%20personalization%20options%20and%20seasonal%20momentum%20can%20converge%20for%20Starbucks%20to%20%26quot%3Bown%20the%20moment%26quot%3B%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20holiday%20season%20at%20Starbucks%20is%20part%20of%20the%20zeitgeist%2C%20and%20really%2C%20really%20embedded%20into%20our%20annual%20rituals%2C%20in%20many%20respects%2C%26quot%3B%20Della%20Penna%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20something%20for%20everyone%20on%20a%20global%20basis%2C%20which%20makes%20this%20much%20bigger%20than%20a%20domestic%20promotion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fbecc7d-860b-48ba-b7b9-a8689d50eca7%5C%22%3EInnovation%20beyond%20the%20holidays%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Starbucks%20has%20successfully%20embedded%20itself%20in%20seasonal%20rituals%2C%20Jean-Pierre%20Lacroix%2C%20president%20of%20the%20strategic%20design%20agency%2C%20Shikatani%20Lacroix%20Design%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20company's%20continued%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrian-niccol-starbucks-ceo-one-year-road-map-report-card-2025-9%23starbucks-is-working-to-bring-back-its-cozy-cafe-vibe-and-to-streamline-ordering-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBack%20to%20Starbucks%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20effort%20will%20have%20to%20be%20about%20rediscovering%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20repeating%20%E2%80%94%20its%20roots%2C%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20customers%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20exists%2C%26quot%3B%20Lacroix%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20need%20to%20reinvent%20themselves%2C%20not%20just%20go%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperimenting%20with%20new%20regional%20flavors%20is%20a%20good%20start%2C%20and%20the%20holiday%20season%20presents%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20do%20so%20while%20remaining%20culturally%20relevant%2C%20Lacroix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20holiday%20marks%20the%20first%20one%20that%20will%20carry%20the%20full%20weight%20of%20Niccol's%20influence%20since%20he%20became%20CEO%20last%20September%2C%20and%20the%20peak%20season%20presents%20a%20major%20test%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-ceo-brian-niccol-repeat-chipotle-strategy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleadership%20and%20innovation%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20his%20broader%20turnaround%20plan%2C%20Senatore%20said.%20It%20will%20also%20stress-test%20Starbucks'%20Green%20Apron%20Service%20model%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20this%20year%20with%20the%20specific%20goal%20of%20improving%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20innovation%20that%20debuted%20entirely%20under%20Niccol's%20purview%20was%20the%20September%20rollout%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-new-protein-cold-foams-taste-test-better-than-expected-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein%20milks%20and%20cold%20foams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20October's%20earnings%20report%2C%20Starbucks%20said%20that%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-protein-drinks-are-helping-fuel-gains-for-the-chain-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein%20offerings%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20behind%20a%201%25%20rise%20in%20its%20fourth-quarter%20comparable%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20time%20in%20seven%20quarters%20that%20the%20coffee%20chain%20has%20reported%20an%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20t