20in%20illiquid%20private%20funds%2C%20the%20wealthy%20could%20be%20hedge%20funds'%20new%20fundraising%20focus.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%245%20trillion%20hedge%20fund%20industry%20is%20backed%20by%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20pools%20of%20money%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20pensions%2C%20endowments%2C%20and%20sovereign%20wealth%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20big-name%20institutions%20are%20facing%20a%20cash%20crunch%20thanks%20to%20capital%20tied%20up%20in%20illiquid%20private%20equity%20and%20venture%20funds.%20For%20hedge%20funds%20looking%20to%20grow%2C%20there%20are%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20outside%20the%20institutions%20wanting%20in%20on%20the%20action%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20wealth%20%E2%80%94%20which%20refers%20to%20money%20held%20on%20platforms%20run%20by%20the%20private%20banking%20divisions%20of%20places%20like%20Goldman%20as%20well%20as%20wealth%20advice%20giants%20like%20Merrill%20Lynch%2C%20independent%20advisors%2C%20and%20family%20offices%20%E2%80%94%20is%20eager%20to%20invest%20in%20hedge%20funds%20and%20has%20plenty%20of%20capital%20to%20put%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20report%20estimates%20that%20less%20than%20%24500%20billion%20of%20the%20%2450.7%20trillion%20of%20private%20wealth%20assets%20are%20in%20hedge%20funds.%20If%20this%20segment%20of%20capital%20followed%20the%20recommendation%20of%20chief%20investment%20officers%20from%20these%20platforms%20and%20family%20offices%20for%20hedge%20fund%20exposure%2C%20there%20would%20be%20more%20than%20%244%20trillion%20in%20hedge%20fund%20investments%20%E2%80%94%20close%20to%20the%20industry's%20total%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20closing%2010%25%20of%20this%20gap%20would%20double%20the%20current%20assets%26quot%3B%20that%20private%20wealth%20has%20in%20hedge%20funds%2C%20Goldman's%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20big-name%20managers%20that%20have%20already%20tapped%20this%20space.%20Millennium%20has%20sold%20LP%20stakes%20in%20its%20flagship%20fund%20via%20private%20bank%20advisors%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennium-izzy-englander-hedge-fund-future-stake-sale-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffered%20a%20piece%20of%20its%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20wealthy%20clients%20of%20banks%20like%20Goldman%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20and%20UBS.%20Jain%20Global%20tapped%20the%20private%20wealth%20channel%20for%20capital%20before%20launching%20in%20mid-2024.%20Coatue%20and%20Tiger%20Global%20count%20platforms%20like%20JPMorgan's%20private%20bank%20as%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20channel%20is%20hungriest%20for%20more%20hedge%20fund%20exposure%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman's%20report.%20A%20survey%20done%20by%20the%20bank's%20capital%20introduction%20team%20found%20that%2068%25%20of%20private%20bank%20advisors%20and%20RIAs%20wanted%20to%20increase%20their%20hedge%20fund%20bets%20this%20year%2C%20while%20only%204%25%20intended%20to%20cut%20them.%20Meanwhile%2C%20only%2031%25%20of%20pension%20and%20insurance%20investors%20wanted%20to%20put%20more%20into%20hedge%20funds.%20For%20endowments%2C%20foundations%2C%20and%20sovereign%20wealth%20funds%2C%20it%20was%20even%20worse%20%E2%80%94%2030%25%20wanted%20to%20increase%20hedge%20fund%20exposure%20while%2014%25%20wanted%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221d70b08-a40e-4f19-b218-75dc517ee95f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHedge%20funds%20thrive%20in%20chaos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20private%20wealth%20managers%20shunned%20hedge%20funds%2C%20which%20were%20perceived%20to%20have%20high%20fees%20and%20middling%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20choppy%20markets%20and%20higher%20interest%20rates%20since%20the%20pandemic%20have%20led%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bimproved%20image%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20industry%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20rich%20and%20their%20advisors%2C%20Goldman's%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20that%20firms%20have%20made%20money%20too%3A%20Goldman%20notes%20that%20the%20average%20fund%20has%20returned%209.4%25%20annually%20from%202020%20through%20June%20of%202025%2C%20while%20a%2060%2F40%20stocks-bonds%20portfolio%20was%20up%20only%206.6%25%20annually%20over%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20for%20managers%20is%2C%20where%20do%20all%20these%20assets%20go%3F%20The%20industry%20is%20as%20big%20as%20it%20has%20ever%20been%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20well-known%20firms%20are%20closed%20to%20new%20capital%20or%20returning%20money%20to%20investors%20to%20avoid%20becoming%20too%20bloated.%20Marshall%20Wace%20is%20the%20latest%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20give%20%243.1%20billion%20back%20to%20investors%20in%20its%20two%20largest%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firms%20that%20have%20become%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20the%20multistrategy%20behemoths%20that%20now%20have%20headcounts%20in%20the%20thousands%20and%20teams%20based%20around%20the%20world.%20These%20managers%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20established%20track%20records%2C%20such%20as%20Millennium%2C%20Citadel%2C%20and%20Point72%2C%20are%20often%20able%20to%20raise%20assets%20quickly%20but%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-pay-poaching-relocation-mercenaries-buy-loyalty-millennium-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstrained%20by%20a%20lack%20of%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20for%20funds%20seeking%20capital%20and%20willing%20to%20hire%20fundraisers%20focused%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20private%20wealth%20channel%2C%20there%20are%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20available%20for%20the%20taking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wealth%20segment%20offers%20both%20a%20new%20frontier%20and%20a%20formidable%20%E2%80%94%20but%20surmountable%20%E2%80%94%20challenge%20for%20managers.%20Those%20who%20invest%20in%20understanding%20the%20landscape%2C%20building%20the%20right%20capabilities%2C%20and%20fostering%20long-term%20relationships%20will%20be%20best%20positioned%20to%20capture%20this%20wave%20of%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman's%20report%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-wealth-hedge-funds-fundraising-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763721241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691f72c5abd5e944effb2bd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-wealth-hedge-funds-fundraising-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20from%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says%20there%20are%20trillions%20of%20private%20wealth%20assets%20interested%20in%20hedge%20funds.%20They%20could%20give%20funds%20a%20new%20focus%20for%20fundraising.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bsaacks%40businessinsider.com%20(Bradley%20Saacks)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B10%20More%20Days%2C%20Would've%20Changed%20His%20School%26quot%3B%3A%20Father%20On%20Delhi%20Boy's%20Suicide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Class%2010%20student%20of%20a%20prestigious%20Delhi%20school%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20wanted%20to%20enrol%20in%20an%20acting%20school%20in%20Mumbai%20after%20graduation%20and%20enter%20Bollywood.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763721237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-11%2Fc8pr5nn_st-columba-suicide-boy_625x300_21_November_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-student-suicide-st-columbas-school-shourya-patil-teachers-rajendra-place-metro-station-latest-news-9676080%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Class%2010%20student%20of%20a%20prestigious%20Delhi%20school%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20wanted%20to%20enrol%20in%20an%20acting%20school%20in%20Mumb