e%20TikTok%2C%20Reddit%2C%20Pinterest%2C%20or%20Instagram%20to%20find%20information.%20Nearly%20half%20(46%25)%20of%20Gen%20Z%20users%20prefer%20to%20search%20on%20social%20media%20rather%20than%20Google%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20last%20year%20from%20Forbes%20Advisor%20and%20Talker%20Research.%20That%20figure%20generally%20lines%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnearly-half-genz-use-tiktok-instagram-over-google-search-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20own%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Gen%20Z's%20search%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20changing%20online%20search%20landscape%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20consumers%2C%20media%20companies%2C%20advertisers%2C%20and%20tech%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedia-startups-post-google-zero-search-traffic-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EA%20new%20generation%20of%20media%20startups%20is%20built%20to%20survive%20'Google%20Zero'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-search-reshapes-seo-fueling-geo-gold-rush-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20SEO%20is%20GEO%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20no%20one%20really%20knows%20the%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStay%20tuned%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20after%20Google%3A%20How%20the%20search%20giant%20is%20disrupting%20itself%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhy%20Pinterest%20is%20all%20in%20on%20visual%20search%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSocial%20search%20is%20definitely%20a%20hot%20topic%2C%26quot%3B%20Evelyn%20Mitchell-Wolf%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Forrester%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20especially%20as%20%26quot%3Bsearch%20behaviors%20fracture%20or%20distribute%20among%20a%20broader%20array%20of%20platforms%20aside%20from%20just%20Google.%26quot%3B%20In%20fact%2C%20more%20US%20consumers%20are%20turning%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%20than%20to%20AI%20options%2C%20such%20as%20ChatGPT%20or%20Microsoft%20Copilot%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20survey%20from%20EMARKETER%2C%20Business%20Insider's%20sister%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FbRBQd%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Bar%20Chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FbRBQd%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20still%20king%20among%20traditional%20search%20engines%20and%20AI%20search%20tools%2C%20controlling%20around%2090%25%20of%20the%20global%20market%2C%20according%20to%20network%20services%20firm%20Cloudflare.%20Google%20has%20also%20responded%20to%20competition%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-glue-pizza-i-tried-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadding%20AI%20overviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20many%20of%20its%20search%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20earnings%20report%20last%20month%2C%20Google's%20parent%20company%20Alphabet%20said%20quarterly%20sales%20from%20Google%20search%20rose%2015%25%20from%20a%20year%20ago%20to%20%2456.6%20billion%2C%20making%20up%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20company's%20overall%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20market%20dominance%20in%20traditional%20search%20doesn't%20factor%20in%20searches%20on%20video%20apps%20like%20TikTok%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ee-commerce%20tools%20like%20Amazon%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20however.%20And%20Google's%20grip%20on%20the%20overall%20search%20landscape%20could%20loosen%20as%20the%20internet%20splinters%20into%20smaller%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20AI%20chatbots%20and%20video%20apps%2C%