esembled%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fwarby-parker-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarby%20Parker%3C%2Fa%3E%20(funnily%20enough%2C%20Warby%20Parker%20partnered%20with%20Google%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-competing-with-meta-ray-bans-new-warby-parker-partnership-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20rival%20AI%20glasses%20bet%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20walls%20were%20lined%20with%20AI%20glasses%20from%20collaborations%20with%20both%20Oakley%20and%20Ray-Ban.%20These%20glasses%20were%20available%20for%20purchase%2C%20while%20the%20Meta%20Ray-Ban%20Displays%20required%20an%20appointment%20to%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20of%20Meta's%20retail%20innovations%3A%20ping%20pong%20paddle%20mirrors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ping%20pong%20paddle%20mirrors%20at%20Meta%20Lab.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e31e0abd5e944effb13aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20mirrors%20all%20around%20the%20Meta%20Lab%2C%20and%20I%20caught%20more%20than%20one%20customer%20taking%20a%20mirror%20selfie.%20They%20were%20also%20used%20for%20glasses%20demos%20(say%3A%20%26quot%3BHey%20Meta%2C%20take%20a%20picture%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20glasses%20counters%2C%20Meta%20replaced%20the%20traditional%20rubber%20on%20a%20ping%20pong%20paddle%20with%20a%20mirror%20for%20handheld%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pop-up's%20design%20was%20skate-themed.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Zoo%20York%20skateboard%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e3226e1a9cbb014de8e12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20exploring%20the%20wall%20of%20glasses%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20the%20other%20side%2C%20which%20was%20filled%20with%20skateboard-themed%20art.%20The%20collection%20was%20made%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Zoo%20York.%20It%20offered%20viewers%20an%20opportunity%20to%20%26quot%3Btravel%20through%20the%20timeline%20of%20New%20York%20skate%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20a%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20I%20noticed%20how%20quiet%20the%20Meta%20Lab%20was.%20At%2011%3A30%20a.m.%20on%20a%20Wednesday%2C%20it%20likely%20wasn't%20peak%20hours.%20However%2C%20on%20this%20base%20floor%2C%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20twice%20as%20many%20staff%20members%20as%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Meta%20representative%20wrote%20over%20email%20that%20%26quot%3Bfoot%20traffic%20numbers%20have%20exceeded%20expectations%20across%20all%20stores.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETime%20for%20a%20demo!%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Meta%20Lab%20employee%20unboxing%20a%20pair%20of%20Ray-Bans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e3283abd5e944effb13c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20Lab%20is%20built%20for%20AI%20glasses%20demos.%20There%20are%20signs%20scattered%20around%20the%20shop%20suggesting%20prompts%20to%20ask%20your%20glasses.%20Naturally%2C%20I%20signed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20trusty%20Meta%20Lab%20employee%20pulled%20me%20aside%20and%20started%20with%20my%20first%20demo%3A%20the%20second-generation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerberg-meta-ai-glasses-cognitive-disadvantage-q2-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20Ray-Bans%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BHey%20Meta%2C%20take%20a%20picture.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Meta%20Ray-Bans%20in%20a%20mirror.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e32dfabd5e944effb13d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Meta%20Lab%20guide%20walked%20me%20through%20all%20of%20the%20features.%20He%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20play%20music%2C%20how%20to%20ask%20Meta%20AI%20for%20information%2C%20or%20how%20to%20take%20a%20picture.%20Thus%2C%20this%20mirror%20selfie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20showed%20me%20how%20the%20Ray-Bans%20have%20transition%20lenses%20based%20on%20the%20time%20of%20day%20and%20brightness.%20Using%20a%20flashlight%2C%20he%20darkened%20one%20of%20the%20lenses.%20That%2C%20dear%20reader%2C%20is%20why%20it%20looks%20like%20I'm%20wearing%20an%20eyepatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20second%20demo%3A%20The%20higher-tech%20Meta%20Ray-Ban%20Display%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Meta%20neural%20band%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e337889026fbb4d0dfef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20upstairs%2C%20I%20asked%20to%20demo%20the%20Meta%20Ray-Ban%20Display%2C%20which%2C%20as%20their%20name%20suggests%2C%20includes%20an%20integrated%20screen%20in%20the%20glasses%20lens.%20(I%20was%20still%20jealous%20of%20my%20colleague%2C%20Peter%20Kafka%2C%20who%20got%20to%20try%20them%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ray-ban-display-glasses-lens-screen-photos-cost-review-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20September%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20My%20Meta%20Lab%20guide%20sized%20a%20%26quot%3Bneural%20band%26quot%3B%20for%20me%20and%20walked%20me%20through%20its%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20glasses%20are%20controlled%20through%20a%20series%20of%20small%20hand%20motions.%20Users%20tap%20their%20index%20finger%20to%20select%2C%20or%20their%20middle%20finger%20to%20go%20back.%20To%20swipe%2C%20they%20move%20their%20thumb%20back%20and%20forth%20on%20their%20index%20finger%2C%20similar%20to%20a%20joystick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20some%20time%20to%20get%20used%20to.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20pro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Display%20lived%20up%20to%20the%20hype.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20Chandonnet%20is%20pictured%20in%20the%20Meta%20Ray-Ban%20Displays.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e33cae1a9cbb014de8e60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-leaked-smart-glasses-display-announcement-rayban-oakleymeta-connect-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20Ray-Ban%20Display%3C%2Fa%3E%20demo%20was%20fascinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Maps%20feature%20seemed%20helpful%2C%20as%20did%20the%20search%20function.%20The%20quality%20of%20the%20live%20transcription%20was%20more%20varied.%20But%2C%20above%20all%2C%20I%20was%20awed%20by%20the%20tech.%20The%20integrated%20screen%20was%20discreet%2C%20and%20I%20could%20see%20future%20use%20cases.%20Yes%2C%20I%20would%20love%20to%20watch%20Netflix%20on%20the%20subway%20without%20having%20to%20look%20down%20at%20my%20phone.%20Meta%20just%20needs%20to%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20fun%20moment%3A%20Walking%20me%20through%20the%20search%20functions%2C%20my%20Meta%20Lab%20guide%20asked%20me%20to%20pick%20a%20question%20of%20my%20own.%20I%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Meta%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20Displays%20brought%20up%20an%20older%20pick%20of%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20before%20he%20became%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-health-workout-elon-musk-cage-fight-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebroccoli-haired%20Buff%20Zuck%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20told%20my%20guide%3B%20he%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAm%20I%20going%20to%20pay%20%24799%20for%20a%20pair%20of%20Displays%3F%20No.%20The%20tech%20is%20a%20bit%20too%20early%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20sure%20the%20screen%20justifies%20itself%20just%20yet.%20(I'm%20more%20likely%20to%20buy%20the%20simpler%20AI%20Ray-Bans%3B%20I%20liked%20the%20music%20and%20photo%20options.)%20However%2C%20it%20was%20a%20promising%20sign%20of%20what's%20to%20come%20in%20wearable%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELet's%20tour%20the%20upstairs!%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta's%20custom%20Ray-Ban%20cases%20are%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e340ce1a9cbb014de8e6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20finished%20both%20of%20my%20demos%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20tour%20the%20upstairs%20of%20the%20pop-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20up%3A%20the%20custom%20engraving%20bar.%20With%20printers%20in%20the%20back%2C%20customers%20could%20request%20custom%20cases%20for%20their%20glasses%20or%20get%20the%20New%20York-only%20specialty%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20to%20it%20was%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20area%2C%20where%20customers%20could%20request%20coffee%20from%20Buddies%20in%20Williamsburg%20or%20massive%20black-and-white%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20when%20I%20started%20realizing%20how%20much%20money%20Meta%20likely%20spent.%20From%20multiple%20art%20collections%20to%20food%20and%20case%20engravings%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0let%20alone%20the%20prime%20New%20York%20real%20estate%20%E2%80%94%20Meta%20spared%20no%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESpotted%3A%20the%20Meta%20Quest%20headsets.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta's%20Quest%20headsets%20are%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e34a6e1a9cbb014de8e87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20Lab%20was%20almost%20entirely%20devoted%20to%20AI%20glasses.%20They%20covered%20the%20walls%2C%20both%20upstairs%20and%20downstairs%2C%20and%20the%20art%20was%20designed%20for%20use%20with%20the%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20tucked%20into%20a%20nook%20near%20the%20register%2C%20customers%20could%20find%20another%20Meta%20hardware%20bet%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fmeta-quest-3s-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20Quest%3C%2Fa%3E%20VR%20headsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20of%20the%20glasses%20were%20hooked%20up%20to%20demo%20tablets.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20demo%20at%20Meta%20Lab%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e3522abd5e944effb144b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20Meta%20Lab%20felt%20like%20a%20hybrid%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-store%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20Sunglass%20Hut.%20Some%20of%20the%20glasses%20were%20connected%20to%20tablets%20for%20a%20demonstration%2C%20which%20was%20helpful%20when%20human%20Meta%20workers%20weren't%20available%20to%20assist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%2C%20Meta%20employees%20were%20everywhere.%20With%20only%20a%20few%20customers%20browsing%20the%20pop-up%2C%20many%20staffers%20were%20chatting%20among%20themselves.%20There%20was%20even%20a%20Meta%20elevator%20attendant%20whose%20job%20was%20to%20press%201%20or%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20the%20Meta%20Lab%20was%20more%20overstaffed%20than%20under-trafficked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20Meta%20AI%20use%3A%20creating%20custom%20stickers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta%20Lab's%20%26quot%3BSticker%20Slam%26quot%3B%20is%20pictured.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e3789e1a9cbb014de8ef5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20Meta%20Lab's%20goal%20is%20to%20show%20customers%20new%20and%20exciting%20use%20cases%20for%20the%20company's%20AI%2C%20beyond%20generating%20recipes%20and%20email%20drafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20Meta%20AI's%20image%20generator%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BSticker%20Slam%26quot%3B%20offers%20customers%20the%20chance%20to%20create%20their%20own%20AI-generated%20images.%20I%20asked%20for%20my%20dog%2C%20Charlotte%2C%20with%20angel%20wings%20and%20a%20tiara.%20The%20machine%20nailed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEvan%20Mock%20designed%20much%20of%20the%20top%20floor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Art%20designed%20by%20Evan%20Mock%20is%20pictured%20in%20Meta%20Lab.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e38cae1a9cbb014de8f2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeeping%20with%20the%20skate%20theme%2C%20actor%20and%20skateboarder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgossip-girl-evan-mock-tom-holland-dream-guest-star-interview-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEvan%20Mock%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20much%20of%20the%20top%20floor.%20The%20colors%20were%20all%20neon%2C%20and%20there%20were%20name%20plates%20plastered%20around%20a%20map%20of%20New%20York%20with%20Mock's%20memorable%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20display%20featured%20some%20print%20magazines%20in%20which%20Mock%20was%20featured%20on%20the%20cover.%20This%20wasn't%20the%20Lab's%20first%20reference%20to%20magazines.%20Downstairs%2C%20one%20of%20the%20Meta%20AI%20prompts%20asked%20the%20glasses%20where%20to%20buy%20skateboarding%20magazines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spotted%20a%20copy%20of%20%3Cem%3EV%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20of%20my%20first%20jobs%20in%20journalism.%20Print%20media%20isn't%20dead!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELeaving%20the%20Lab%2C%20I%20felt%20hopeful%20for%20Meta's%20hardware%20effort.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Meta%20Logo%20is%20pictured%20in%20the%20design%20of%20the%20pop-up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691e392be1a9cbb014de8f3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Chandonnet%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prepared%20to%20leave%20the%20Lab%2C%20but%20not%20before%20marveling%20at%20the%20subtle%20Meta%20logo%20carved%20into%20the%20pop-up's%20high%20wooden%20arch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20me%20to%20wonder%3A%20Could%20part%20of%20the%20Lab's%20relative%20slowness%20during%20my%20visit%20have%20to%20do%20with%20the%20pop-up's%20%26quot%3BMeta%20Lab%26quot%3B%20branding%3F%20American%20shoppers%20could%20certainly%20recognize%20the%20company's%20mega-popular%20products%2C%20such%20as%20the%20classic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-logo-change-blue-1600-word-memo-meta-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblue%20Facebook%20logo%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20the%20rainbow%20Instagram%20camera.%20But%20how%20many%20could%2