%20founded%20in%202014%2C%20leased%20apartments%20and%20hotel%20rooms%20in%20bulk%2C%20redesigned%20them%20with%20a%20minimalist%20aesthetic%2C%20and%20rented%20them%20to%20travelers.%20It's%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Canadian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsonder-marriott-bankruptcy-cofounder-ceo-francis-davidson-shocked-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrancis%20Davidson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20is%20the%20ideal%20of%20a%202010s%20founder%3A%20VC-backed%2C%20college%20dropout%2C%20Forbes%2030%20Under%2030.%20He%20offered%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsonder-spac-ceo-francis-davidson-short-term-rentals-travel-hospitality-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevolutionary%26quot%3B%20promise%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Goodbye%2C%20poorly%20decorated%20Airbnbs%20with%20quirky%20hosts.%20Hello%2C%20streamlined%20rentals%20managed%20with%20modern%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202024%2C%20he%20unveiled%20his%20pi%C3%A8ce%20de%20r%C3%A9sistance%3A%20a%20deal%20between%20Sonder%20and%20blue-chip%20Marriott%2C%20which%20was%20heralded%20as%20a%20way%20to%20bring%20that%20vision%20into%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20this%20deal%20happen%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20multi-party%2C%20complex%20capital%20raise%20I%20orchestrated%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20hardest%20thing%20I've%20ever%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20CEO%20Davidson%20wrote%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20analysts%20lauded%20the%20deal%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20would%20add%209%2C000%20rooms%20to%20Marriott's%20portfolio%20%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20figure%20for%20the%20hotel%20giant's%20valuation.%20Sonder%20said%20after%20the%20deal%20closed%20it%20would%20reduce%20costs%20by%20as%20much%20as%20%2450%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20the%20Marriott%20deal%20was%20maybe%20less%20of%20a%20legitimization%20and%20more%20of%20a%20Hail%20Mary.%20Since%20going%20public%20at%20a