receive%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20if%20I%20met%20the%20target%20of%20promoting%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20sales.%20This%20income%20was%20not%20fixed%2C%20and%20they%20required%20me%20to%20relocate%2025%20km%20away.%20I%20attempted%20to%20do%20this%20work%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20but%20it%20became%20unsustainable%20because%20I%20also%20had%20to%20manage%20my%20field%20responsibilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20fertilisers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20and%20fertilisers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20run%20a%20business%20from%20the%20village%2C%20he%20started%20a%20nursery%20by%20selling%20moringa%20and%20mango%20saplings.%20However%2C%20this%20business%20would%20peak%20onl